<div id="review_3136543010" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3136543010" />
    <a title="Laurene" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3628266-laurene"><img alt="Laurene" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1487357434p2/3628266.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3136543010?book_show_action=true">Jan 18, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Laurene" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Laurene" href="/user/show/3628266-laurene">Laurene</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780385501200" href="/book/show/984003.A_Painted_House">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3136543010" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8614846563117430062"> John Grisham is known for his legal thrillers. But it is in my opinion, his writing away from his usual subject matter -- enlightens his readers to his masterful writing. A Painted House, which I revisited this year, to me, is one of his best. I will never look or eat tomatoes in the same way again!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

